name: Subspace Subway
description:
You want to become a subspace subway driver. In order to get your license, you need to get to light speed in a limited amount of time. Luckily for you the faster you travel the slower time becomes. Dodge space debris and black holes that will slow you down.

Controls Move:
Up and Down Keys
Mouse Click
Finger
